'''= a site where you can help an artificial intelligence learn about the world we live in.'''


URL = http://commons.media.mit.edu:3000/


=Description=

"Computers don't currently know the basic things about the world we consider common sense. Here, you can work with other users to build a database of such knowledge by filling in simple English sentences. The computer will analyze the pieces of these sentences to connect objects and concepts, and draw new conclusions from the things you teach it."
(http://commons.media.mit.edu:3000/)


